high_descs: Walk straight, turn left when you reach the fridge, walk straight and turn right when you reach the stove and walk straight to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the apple inside the kitchen sink.
Turn left to face the microwave.
Open the microwave door, place the apple on the plate inside the microwave and cook the apple.
Turn around, walk straight, and turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the cooked apple inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked apple inside the fridge.

high_descs: Move forward, then turn left to approach the counter to the left of the stove, then turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the apple from inside of the sink.
Turn left to face the microwave.
Cook the apple in the microwave.
Turn around, go straight, and then turn left to face the fridge.
Place the apple inside of the fridge, in front of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple inside of the fridge.

high_descs: Walk forward and left to the kitchen sink
Pick up the red apple from the kitchen sink
Turn left to face the microwave on the counter
Cook the apple in the microwave and then remove it
Turn around and walk to the fridge
Put the apple in the fridge in front of the tomato
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked apple in the fridge
